==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Originary
<hw>O*rig"i*na*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>originarius</ets>: cf. F. <ets>originaire</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Causing existence; productive.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The production of animals, in the <qex>originary</qex> way,
requires a certain degree of warmth.</q> <rj><qau>Cheyne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Primitive; primary; original.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The grand <qex>originary</qex> right of all rights.</q>
<rj><qau>Hickok.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Originate</ent>⟦br⟧
